docs {
  Delta Check worklist. Raising a check (see "01 Reporting Worklist" → Raise
  Delta Check) lives on the report itself; this folder covers the worklist's
  own list and status updates (its own New → Reviewed → Re-Run/Accepted →
  Completed vocabulary, distinct from the other four worklists).
}
